title: Necklace
medium: Glass (molded and carved), white metal, leather, silk, brass
description: Necklace (a) of Twenty-nine rectangular clear plaques, each surmounted by a satin-finished and sculptured parakeet with head turned to left and a long slender pointed tail; plaques strung on fine silver chain with three small silver rings between plaques; small silver spring clasp. Case (b) covered in deep blue leather; cover lined with white satin stamped in gold; deep blue velvet support for necklace.
name: Necklace
